---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SEOHead from '../../components/SEOHead.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import FAQSchema from '../../components/FAQSchema.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <SEOHead slot="head" title="Tattoo Studio Health Compliance — Checklists, Autoclave Logs &amp; Inspections" description="InkFlow's health compliance software helps tattoo studios stay inspection-ready with digital checklists, autoclave logs, and documentation. Built into your studio management. Start free." />
  <FAQSchema questions={[
    { question: "Does InkFlow generate health inspection checklists?", answer: "Yes. Built-in checklists cover sterilization, cleanliness, and documentation requirements. Customize for your local health department's requirements." },
    { question: "Can I log autoclave cycles?", answer: "Yes. Digital autoclave logs with date, time, cycle type, and operator. Export for health department inspections." },
    { question: "Are compliance records stored permanently?", answer: "Yes. All compliance records are stored with timestamps and audit trails. Exportable for inspections at any time." },
  ]} />
  <Navbar />

  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 sm:pt-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-accent-400 mb-3">TATTOO HEALTH COMPLIANCE</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-5xl">Tattoo Health Compliance: Stay Inspection-Ready with Digital Checklists</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-400">InkFlow's health compliance software keeps your studio inspection-ready with digital checklists, autoclave logs, and documentation. Health inspections don't have to be stressful.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="https://app.ink-flows.com/register" class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-ink-950 hover:bg-accent-400 transition-all">Try InkFlow Free →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 bg-ink-900/20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Why Compliance Software Matters for Tattoo Studios</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Health inspections are stressful when you're not prepared.</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Paper checklists get lost or outdated. InkFlow's digital checklists are always current and accessible from any device.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Autoclave logs are easy to forget — and impossible to backfill.</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Digital autoclave logging means every cycle is recorded automatically. No more scrambling before an inspection.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Missing compliance records can shut you down.</h3><p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Health departments require years of documentation. InkFlow stores everything permanently with full audit trails.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Compliance Features Built for Tattoo Studios</h2>
      <div class="mt-12 space-y-16">
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 items-center">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Digital Health Inspection Checklists</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">Built-in checklists cover sterilization, cleanliness, and documentation. Customizable for your local health department's requirements.</p>
          <h4 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Customizable Per Location</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Each studio location can have its own checklist based on local regulations. Templates included for common health department standards.</p>
          <h5 class="mt-3 text-base font-medium text-white">Completed Checklist Sign-Off</h5>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Each checklist requires staff sign-off with timestamp. Managers review and approve. Full accountability for every inspection item.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-ink-900/50 border border-ink-800 p-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">[Screenshot: Compliance dashboard]</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1 rounded-xl bg-ink-900/50 border border-ink-800 p-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">[Screenshot: Autoclave log]</p>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Digital Autoclave Logs with Audit Trail</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400">Log every autoclave cycle with date, time, cycle type, and operator. Export for inspections at any time.</p>
          <h4 class="mt-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Cycle Tracking with Sterilization Verification</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Record temperature, pressure, and cycle duration. Attach spore test results digitally. Everything an inspector needs.</p>
          <h5 class="mt-3 text-base font-medium text-white">Export-Ready Reports</h5>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Generate inspection-ready reports in seconds. Filter by date range, operator, or equipment. No paper shuffling before an audit.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BUYER GUIDE -->
  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 bg-ink-900/20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white text-center">Which Compliance Approach Fits Your Studio?</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-center text-gray-400">The right choice depends on your local regulations and inspection frequency.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Solo artist with annual inspections</h3><p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Paper logs might pass inspection, but one mistake can mean a citation. InkFlow's digital checklists ensure you're always ready.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Multi-artist studio with frequent audits</h3><p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Each artist needs to log autoclave cycles and daily checklists. InkFlow centralizes compliance so you can spot issues before inspectors do.</p></div>
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Multi-location chain</h3><p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-1">Each location has different inspectors and requirements. InkFlow's per-location checklists with centralized reporting keep every location compliant.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="border-t border-ink-800/50 py-16 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Never Dread an Inspection Again</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-400">Free plan includes basic compliance checklists. Upgrade for full autoclave logging and audit reports.</p>
    <a href="https://app.ink-flows.com/register" class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-lg bg-accent-500 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-ink-950 hover:bg-accent-400 transition-all">Try InkFlow Free →</a>
  </section>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
